name: Elm-duotris
tagline: A duotris clone written in elm.
body:
# elm-duotris

This is a clone of the [Duotris game](http://www.binaryzoo.com/duotris_page/) developed by [binary zoo](http://www.binaryzoo.com/). It is written in [elm](http://elm-lang.org/). You can [try it here.](http://dreuter.github.io/elm-duotris/try)

Controls are as follows:
* Left - h
* Right - l
* Down - k
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
